      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS. This example is paired with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox, ensuring a pure analog driving experience. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including professional reinforcement of the rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure optimal cam timing. The suspension retains its factory composure, and the M-variable differential lock provides predictable lock-up under lateral acceleration. While the exterior shows the light patina of a well-enjoyed enthusiast vehicle, the drivetrain remains in peak operating condition, delivering a linear power band all the way to its 8,000 RPM redline.",
