      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-loved 2019 Audi S5 Sportback in Mythos Black Metallic. This car has been my pride and joy, serving as a reliable and exhilarating daily driver. The exterior paint retains a beautiful luster and has been regularly waxed, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side alloy wheel consistent with careful use. Inside, the Magma Red Nappa leather interior remains supple and vibrant; the cabin is smoke-free, and all electronic features\u2014including the Bang & Olufsen sound system and the Virtual Cockpit\u2014are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in great shape with a complete service history from Audi-certified technicians. The turbocharged V6 delivers smooth power, and the transmission shifts crisply. It recently passed a comprehensive multi-point inspection and sits on tires with plenty of tread remaining. This is a solid, honest car for a buyer looking for luxury performance without the new-car price tag.",
